			<PolyStyle>
				<color>40ffffff</color>
			</PolyStyle>
			<BalloonStyle>
				<text>Frog’s Hollow
GPS -37.816546, 144.754355
MELWAYS REF. 39 A-9
LOCATION: Creek at the end of distribution drive
ENTRANCE: 1.5m ×3 ⭕
OTHER SHAPES: ☹
CLAN ZONE: South west
TRANSPORT: Watergardens train to Sunshine. Bus to corner of Boundary / Robinsons Rd
VALUE: ☹
HIGHLIGHT: Triple barrel junction rooms
CLEANLINESS: 🙂
PROBLEMS: 🙂
⛔: 🙂
NEARBY: Wind Tunnel, Snakepit &amp; Dodgy’s Tomb
NOTES: All 3 barrels eventually connect at a grille-room which then goes into a quad-barrel and out into the creek again.
Named after all the noise of the frogs in the area.</text>
			</BalloonStyle>
		</Style>
	</gx:CascadingStyle>
