				<width>3</width>
			</LineStyle>
			<PolyStyle>
				<color>40ffffff</color>
			</PolyStyle>
			<BalloonStyle>
				<text>The Maze
🍸
GPS: -37.823213, 145.023108
MELWAYS REF: 45 A-11
LOCATION: Next to flats on west side of Evansdale Rd between railway place and Austin Street over wooden fence.
ENTRANCE: 3.2m ⚪
OTHER SHAPES: ⌂, balloon, ⬜, ⌂ &amp; ⬜
CLAN ZONE: East.
TRANSPORT: Train to Hawthorn
HIGHLIGHT: Length &amp; changes. One of the top 3 drains in Australia.
WATER: 🙂
CLEANLINESS: Avoidable wet feet.
PROBLEMS: Doing it in one visit.
VALUE: 🏆
NEARBY: The Slide, Mega Slide, Ladders to Heaven, No Vest, Vampire&apos;s Cavern, CBRBD &amp; Punctual.
NOTES: Do this drain on a nice hot day. There are a few exits &amp; many junctions &amp; features. A 10/10er. Bike can be used in sections. Follow white arrows where possible.
Maze is named due to the many splits and loops in the system.</text>
			</BalloonStyle>
		</Style>
	</gx:CascadingStyle>
