MELWAYS REF. 181 J-11
LOCATION: South side of Coopers St east of the Northern Hospital.
VALUE: 🗑
ENTRANCE: 1.7m ⭕
OTHER SHAPES: ☹
CLAN ZONE: North
TRANSPORT: South Morang train to Epping.
CLEANLINESS: Was muddy during works.
NEARBY: Lalor, Pondage, Mill Park &amp; Kanish’s Tomb.
PROBLEMS: Hard to get into.
HIGHLIGHT: ?
NOTES: Was flooded during construction. At time of print it had been checked but report wasn’t recorded.
