			<BalloonStyle>
				<text>Underpass
ⓘ
GPS -37.931585, 145.156431
MELWAYS REF. 80 A-4
LOCATION: Next to John Allison Monkhouse on the west side of Springvale Rd, north of Police Rd
ENTRANCE: 1.8m ×2 ⬜
OTHER SHAPES: ⭕
CLAN ZONE: South
CLEANLINESS: Wet feet
VALUE: 😐
