HIGHLIGHT: Outlet
PROBLEMS: Trying to exit at the outlet
⛔: Wet feet
NEARBY: Polluted, Rambo, Nazi, Fall, Sandown Park &amp; Exit
NOTES: Only a short tunnel. Don’t fall into pit at the outlet.
Underpass is so called because it just runs under a couple of roads and a large block.</text>
