			</PolyStyle>
			<BalloonStyle>
				<text>Mitchell’s Tomb
GPS -37.703716, 145.12847
MELWAYS REF: 21 E-2
LOCATION: North east side of St Helena Rd in Leith Park just north east of Dugong Ct. Next to Tiffani’s
VALUE: 🗑
ENTRANCE: 1.3m ⭕
OTHER SHAPES: ☹
CLAN ZONE: North east
TRANSPORT: Car
⛔🙂
HIGHLIGHT: Grilled room
PROBLEMS: Long, low &amp; boring
CLEANLINESS: 😐
NEARBY: Tiffani’s, The Mission &amp; Eltham
NOTES: Prowler stated that this drain should not be added to the Drainguide. Mulletjocks says the outlet is only 0.9m.
Mitchell’s Tomb is named after Prowler’s mate. Prowler sold his first son to the Drain Gods so as he could join the Clan and win the Gold Clannie.</text>
			</BalloonStyle>
