			<description><![CDATA[<div>Ash’s Tomb<br></div><div>🚫<br></div><div>GPS -37.814673, 144.80482<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 40 B-8<br></div><div>LOCATION: Northeast cnr of Boundary Rd &amp; Park West Dve<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North west<br></div><div>⛔ 🙂<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Car<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.5m ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⬜<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Weird flat bottom section<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Fenced off entrance<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Avoidable mud<br></div><div>VALUE: ☹<br></div><div>NEARBY: Jorgee’s Tomb, Snakepit, Wind Tunnel &amp; Frog’s Hollow<br></div><div>NOTES: The drain gets bigger &amp; is only low for the last 5 minutes.<br></div><div>Named after the explorer from the late 1990’s.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
