		<Placemark id="5984C714B9000034">
			<name>Stony Creek</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Stony Creek<br></div><div>🚫 👁<br></div><div>GPS -37.688766, 144.984236<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 41 A-2<br></div><div>LOCATION: Corner of Matthew &amp; Duke Streets. Hill Reserve.<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.6m ×2 ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⬜<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: South west<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Square section<br></div><div>⛔: Chest<br></div><div>VALUE: 🗑<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Watergardens train to Sunshine<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Filthy water<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: The whole tunnel<br></div><div>NEARBY: Jorgee’s, 50th &amp; Not 50th<br></div><div>NOTES: This drain should be killed, although Gold Clannie winner Bathory liked it.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
