			<name>Tac</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Tac<br></div><div>🚫 🔑<br></div><div>GPS -37.630581, 144.957872<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 180 G-6<br></div><div>LOCATION: Located near where the Oherns Rd ford crosses the Merri Creek (west bank) under the power-lines<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2.4m ⭕<br></div><div>VALUE: 🏆<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Car<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Split<br></div><div>⛔: 🙂<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Locating Tic, Tac &amp; Toe<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Muddy entrance<br></div><div>NEARBY: Grilles in the Mist, COAD, Tic &amp; Toe<br></div><div>NOTES: Do with Nearby Drains.<br></div><div>Tic, Tac &amp; Toe were all found on the same day.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
