			<name>Tenth</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Tenth<br></div><div>🍸<br></div><div>GPS -37.779, 145.081581<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 46 K-1<br></div><div>LOCATION: On the south-east corner of Thompsons Rd &amp; Eastern Fwy junction near Park &amp; Ride<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 4.2m ⌒<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⭕<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North east<br></div><div>VALUE: 🏆<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Water at end<br></div><div>⛔: The outlet is knee deep for the last 5 minutes<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: The size. Room near start<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: 🙂<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Tram 24 or 48 to end of line then bus or walk<br></div><div>NEARBY: Flat &amp; Fisted<br></div><div>NOTES: Remove your shoes to avoid wet outlet. Side tunnels are good.<br></div><div>Tenth was the tenth drain discovered by the Clan.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
