		<Placemark id="5984C714B9000039">
			<name>Grilles In The Mist</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Grilles In The Mist<br></div><div>🚫 🔑<br></div><div>GPS -37.64932, 144.946335<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 180 D-11<br></div><div>LOCATION: East side of Link Rd just south of corner of Foden Ave / Somerton Park Dve<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.5m ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ☹<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: The grilles<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Mucky first 5 meters<br></div><div>⛔: Wide but avoidable at start<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Craigieburn train to Roxburgh Park then walk<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Out of the way<br></div><div>VALUE: ☹<br></div><div>NEARBY: Tic, Tac, Funnel Web’s Lair &amp; COAD<br></div><div>NOTES: Soon gets bigger (2.1m) and has a neat feature at the end. In 2017 Iso demanded an upgrade from 🗑 to ☹.<br></div><div>Grilles in the Mist is a take on the movie Gorillas In The Mist.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
			<styleUrl>#__managed_style_0920FA33F53E916505AE</styleUrl>
			<Point>
				<coordinates>144.946335,-37.64932,0</coordinates>
			</Point>
		</Placemark>
		<Placemark id="5984C714B900003A">
			<name>Guinea Pigs Tomb</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Guinea Pigs Tomb<br></div><div>🚫 🚲 🍸<br></div><div>GPS -37.803459, 145.173291<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 48 E-5<br></div><div>LOCATION: North side of footbridge over Eastern Freeway<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2.2m ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ☹<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North east<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Room at the end<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: 🙂<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Ringwood train to Nunawading then walk<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Exit at end is likely blocked (see notes)<br></div><div>VALUE: 🙂<br></div><div>NEARBY: ☹<br></div><div>NOTES: Nice short pipe that once exited at Springvale Rd, but probably doesn’t now due to freeway extension.<br></div><div>The Guinea Pig’s Tomb is named after the draining clique from the late 90s / early 2000s.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
