			<name>Hoppers Crossing</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Hoppers Crossing<br></div><div>🚫 🚲 🍸<br></div><div>GPS -37.867723, 144.713348<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 203 A-11<br></div><div>LOCATION: Next to the sharp bend on Hawthorn Drive<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2.1m ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ☹<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: South west<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Werribee train to Hoppers Crossing<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Grilled room<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: 🙂<br></div><div>VALUE: 🗑<br></div><div>⛔: Use rocks to avoid getting wet feet at start<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: See waterlevel<br></div><div>NEARBY: Idiot Box<br></div><div>NOTES: The 3 Hopper’s Crossing drains (inc Piggery &amp; Porridge) are all fairly average.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
