		<Placemark id="5984C714B900003F">
			<name>Forgotten</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Forgotten<br></div><div>🚫<br></div><div>GPS -37.751344, 145.030917<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 31 C-3<br></div><div>LOCATION: Follow west bank of Darebin Ck with the flow from Bell St until you come to a double RCP underpass. Go in. Follow creek 50 meters.<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2.5m squashed ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⬜<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North<br></div><div>VALUE: 😐<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: South Morang train to Bell then bus, or Eltham train to Heidelberg then bus<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Plastic tunnel, slide &amp; hand rail<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS &amp; ⛔: OK, unless you slip<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: You’ll most likely slip. If your shoes get wet, the tunnel turns into a slippery slide<br></div><div>NEARBY: Northlands, Northcote Tech Darkies, Coffin &amp; Donaldson Ck<br></div><div>NOTES: The plastic section, buckling at the joins, seems to be a “practice tunnel” for the water-board. The tunnel started 150 meters further along until 1991 when the plastic section was built.<br></div><div>Asked why Woody didn’t tell us about this drain earlier, he replied, “I’d forgotten”.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
			<styleUrl>#__managed_style_0920FA33F53E916505AE</styleUrl>
			<Point>
				<coordinates>145.0309424867562,-37.75165045395167,0</coordinates>
			</Point>
		</Placemark>
		<Placemark id="5984C714B9000040">
			<name>Franger</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Franger<br></div><div>🔑 👤 👁<br></div><div>GPS -38.145988, 145.118226<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 100A A8<br></div><div>LOCATION: Just beside the boat ramp<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.0m ⬜<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⭕<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: South<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Waterfalls &amp; rooms<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Train to Frankston<br></div><div>⛔: Shin to knee<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Wet feet<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Passing the baffle at the start, Grille may be locked. Waterfall has no safety chain<br></div><div>NEARBY: Frankston<br></div><div>VALUE: 😐<br></div><div>NOTES: Be stealthy when using the outlet or grille located at 18 Heatherhill Rd -38.158382, 145.138260<br></div><div>Franger is the nick name for the suburb of Frankston.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
