			<name>Frankston</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Frankston<br></div><div>🚫 👁<br></div><div>GPS -38.139972, 145.121298<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 102 C1<br></div><div>LOCATION: South of Beach St footbridge over Kananook Ck<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2.0m ⬜<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⭕<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: South<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Columns just inside<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Train to Frankston<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Wet feet<br></div><div>⛔: Shin deep<br></div><div>VALUE: 🗑<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Not very good<br></div><div>NEARBY: Franger<br></div><div>NOTES: You need to get wet &amp; the drain is very boring. Frankston works in 2013/14 may have affected the drain.<br></div>]]></description>
