		<Placemark id="5984C714B9000043">
			<name>Funnel Web</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Funnel Web<br></div><div>🚫 🔑 👁<br></div><div>GPS -37.65192, 144.910102<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 179 H8<br></div><div>LOCATION: Grille (locked?) in park near White Ct (hard to find)<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.6m ⭕<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North<br></div><div>VALUE: 🗑<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Car<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Funnel Web’s Lair<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Very long 1.6m RCP<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Low (webby) &amp; flooded entrance<br></div><div>⛔: Deep!<br></div><div>NEARBY: Funnel Web’s Lair &amp; COAD<br></div><div>NOTES: Funnel Web’s Lair &amp; Funnel Web is actually the same drain. The reason they have been added as 2 is that Funnel Web takes in about the first 97% of the drain &amp; is everything that is low, wet, webby, long etc, not worth doing! Funnel Web’s Lair takes in the last 3% (see Funnel Web’s Lair’s notes).<br></div><div>Funnel Web is the drain that leads to Funnel Web’s Lair.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
