			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Trinity’s Tomb &amp; Arachnophobia<br></div><div>ⓘ 🚲<br></div><div>GPS -37.867846, 145.235516<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 63 J-11<br></div><div>LOCATION: North of the Burwood Hwy just west of Stud Rd<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.7m ×2 ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⬜<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: East<br></div><div>⛔: Annoyingly wide but avoidable<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Pointy grille room<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: 🙂<br></div><div>VALUE: ☹<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Bus from Boronia Station to Knox Shopping Centre<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: See waterlevel (⛔)<br></div><div>NOTES: There are a couple of crap drains downstream of Trinity’s Tomb that may be included in the next edition.<br></div><div>NEARBY: Arachnophobia<br></div><div>Trinity’s Tomb is named after the Clan member from the 1980s.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
