			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Key Law Downs<br></div><div>🚫 🚲 🍸<br></div><div>GPS -37.712327, 144.811132<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 14 D-6<br></div><div>LOCATION: Next to 2 Denbigh Ct, Keilor<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2m ⭕<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North west<br></div><div>VALUE: 🗑<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: The entrance<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: 🙂<br></div><div>⛔: 🙂<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Bus or car<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Boring &amp; out of the way<br></div><div>NEARBY: Roxy’s Tomb<br></div><div>NOTES: Nice entrance, but that’s about it! Short Shrinker.<br></div><div>This drain was temporarily called Keilor Downs… for ten years. Coming up with a cool name just didn’t happen.<br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
