			<description><![CDATA[<div>Docklands<br></div><div>🚫 🧠 👁<br></div><div>GPS -37.821429, 144.94149<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 2E E-7<br></div><div>LOCATION: Under wharf into Yarra<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.6 ⬜<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⭕<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: Inner<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Waterlevel is near roof. Risk of being trapped by tide<br></div><div>⛔: Too close to roof for boat. Li-low or swim in<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Walk from Southern Cross Station<br></div><div>VALUE: 🗑<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Conquered by only a few<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Wet Wet Wet!<br></div><div>NEARBY: Bob’s Tomb, City, Nexus, 69er &amp; Melbourne<br></div><div>NOTES: Quite hard as it is under water at high tide &amp; even at low tide is hard to spot! Probably more populated now.<br></div><div>Suggested for deletion. Needs outlet pin-pointed &amp; info regarding tides or location will be deleted.<br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
