			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div><i></i>Dodgy’s Tomb<br></div><div>🚲 🍸<br></div><div>GPS -37.810145, 144.750421<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 360 K-7<br></div><div>LOCATION: NW corner of Boundary &amp; Robinsons Rds<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2.0 ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ☹<br></div><div>VALUE: 🙂<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: South west<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Watergardens train to Sunshine. Bus to corner of Boundary/Robinsons Rd<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: It gets bigger – 2.7m!<br></div><div>⛔: 🙂<br></div><div>NEARBY: Frog’s Hollow, Chocolate Mousse &amp; Wind Tunnel<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: 🙂<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: 🙂<br></div><div>NOTES: Double barrel drain with a large junction room &amp; various crossover rooms.<br></div><div>Grilles via small sidepipes.<br></div><div>Named after the dodgy cross-dressing Biggest Coward winning westie drain finding superstar of the 2010’s – Dodgy!<br></div><div><br></div><div><i></i><br></div>]]></description>
