NOTES: Park in car-park on bend where Lincoln and Elizabeth Streets meet at Map 60 C-6 (-37.849151, 145.073808). On a hot summer&apos;s day, Dougo&apos;s, Sloth&apos;s and Great Stairway is the best day of draining available.
Sloth&apos;s Tomb is named after the co-founding member of the Cave Clan. He is also known as Big Bad.</description>
