				<snippet></snippet>
				<description>Twin 5&apos; RCP&apos;s with 7&apos; &amp; 6&apos; junction rooms and 6&apos; RCP section.
The RCP&apos;s are not placed parallel/side by side. Instead they jut out and butt into it each other at weird angles for the entire length of the drain. Makes for interesting bends and turns!</description>
