			<Placemark id="595366DC2173CFB0CB3D6">
				<name>Adult Swim</name>
				<snippet></snippet>
				<description>Drain running underneath the Western Line, a park, and Blacktown
               Hospital. Begins as 4x 4.5ft square outfalls and then becoming 2x
               separate low but wide 4.5ft x 9ft concrete culverts which do not
               seem to connect upstream. Finally, drain becomes a 6ft RCP and
               shrinks to 4.5ft thereafter for about 150m</description>
				<LookAt>
					<longitude>150.9180731668933</longitude>
					<latitude>-33.77268262652496</latitude>
					<altitude>0</altitude>
					<heading>1.162642222144944e-09</heading>
					<tilt>0</tilt>
