			<Folder id="C3F12DD18A73CFB0CB3D6">
				<name>Ghost Train</name>
				<snippet></snippet>
				<styleUrl>#__managed_style_05D0D2A5813E916505B0</styleUrl>
				<Placemark id="C59DAB756013CFB0CB3D6">
					<name>Ghost Train</name>
					<snippet></snippet>
					<description>The Urban Exploration Collection. Compiled from online sources.
Type: Drain
Interest: Excellent
Features:Short but good drain, two changes. From downstream end: Twin 5.5&apos; rect arched roof on wide canal, with bars accross (the ghost train section), then the huge bit, which is about 10&apos; high. Only about about 400m.  Lots of stuff hanging off the bars, hence the name.
Other comments:
http://www.urbanadventure.org/main/drains/uacity/ghosttrain/ghosttrain.htm</description>
					<LookAt>
						<longitude>151.0393780762623</longitude>
						<latitude>-33.86195730435066</latitude>
						<altitude>0</altitude>
						<heading>0.003898956214460564</heading>
