					<name>3 Pits?</name>
					<snippet></snippet>
					<description>The Urban Exploration Collection. Compiled from online sources.
Type: Drain
Interest: Unexplored
Features: Unexplored - Down channel from &quot;Predator&apos;s&quot;, ie off Sydney Steel Rd. Also Sth of embankment of rail line between Sydenham &amp; Marrickville at  Fraser Park. This canal goes to Cooks river next to Tempe station
Other comments:
http://urbanadventure.org/main/drains/uacity/d_mreps.htm</description>
