					<snippet></snippet>
					<description>GPS:  33°45&apos;56.66&quot;S 151°16&apos;46.28&quot;E
Type: Drain
Rating: 
Info: This drain a surprisingly no graffiti inside, it starts off as a large arch, then opens into a canal, follow it upstream, Lookout for Eels swimming around. A set of twin RCP pipes take you to a dead end chamber, with a stage like platform in it.</description>
