					<name>Crestwood High Hopes</name>
					<snippet></snippet>
					<description>GPS:  33°44&apos;19.82&quot;S 150°58&apos;35.17&quot;E
Type:  Drain
Rating: 0/5
Info:  This drain is a Massive RCP, maybe 2.2m high. I had to use a inflatable raft to get inside, once inside about 15m in it splits into 2 backbreaker 1m high RCPs. Which are just shrinkers. Was disappointed. Save yourself the trouble.</description>
