			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><br></p><div>Tiffani’s Tomb<br></div><div><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;">🔑</span><br></div><div>GPS -37.703716, 145.128476<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 21 E-2<br></div><p><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><br></p><div>LOCATION: East side of Eidlich Road north of Karingal Drive<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.4m <span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;">⭕</span><br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: <span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;">⬜</span><br></div><p><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><br></p><div>CLAN ZONE: North east<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: <span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;">🙂</span><br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Low sections<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Grille room<br></div><p><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><br></p><div>VALUE: <span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif;">☹</span><br></div><div><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;">⛔</span> <span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;">🙂</span><br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Eltham train to Greensborough then bus<br></div><p><br></p><p class="MsoNormal">NEARBY: Eltham, Mitchell’s, The Mission &amp; Kalparrin
Funnel<br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><br></p><div>NOTES: Inlet may be locked.<br></div><div>Tiffani’s is named after the discoverer’s daughter.<br></div><p><br></p><div><br></div>]]></description>
