			<name>Snakepit</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Snakepit<br></div><div>GPS -37.823925, 144.783266<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 39 H-11<br></div><div>LOCATION: Update required. 1 of the 4 tunnels in William Angliss Dve retarding basin just west of Fitzgerald Rd.<br></div><div>VALUE: ☹<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: South west<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.4m ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⬜<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Car<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Grille<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Muddy outlet<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Fairly long. Outlet now on private property. ⛔ Shin deep outlet.<br></div><div>NEARBY: Wind Tunnel &amp; Ash’s Tomb<br></div><div>NOTES: Use manhole to avoid muddy outlet. The retarding basin needs to be checked out.<br></div><div>Snakepit originally finished at a pit that had, when first explored by Cave Clan, a live Eastern Brown snake in it.<br></div>]]></description>
			<styleUrl>#__managed_style_0920FA33F53E916505AE</styleUrl>
