			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Spackas As<br></div><div>GPS -37.880409, 145.272464<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 64 G-11<br></div><div>LOCATION: East side of Rankin Rd<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: East<br></div><div>VALUE: 🙂<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.8m ⭕<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Train to Boronia Station<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Gets bigger<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: A bit webby<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Low section before big section. Can’t exit at outlet<br></div><div>NEARBY: Trinity’s Tomb &amp; Spackas Mayyyte<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: 🙂<br></div><div>NOTES: Not a bad explore. Would be better if you could exit at the outlet.<br></div><div>Name comes from Blind Creek &amp; because the Drainguide had already been printed up to R so the name couldn’t begin with S.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
