		<Placemark id="8682351D963E4617280A">
			<name>Fisted/Casle’s Tomb</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Fisted<br></div><div>GPS -37.755508, 145.092342<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 32 G-4<br></div><div>LOCATION: North side of Templestowe Rd west of Sheahans Rd. Opposite Wonderworld Childcare.<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North east<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2.4m ⭕<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: Wet feet. Scummy water.<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Flooded entrance<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Eltham train to Heidelberg then bus to Helene Street<br></div><div>VALUE: ☹<br></div><div>⛔ Entrance is shin deep<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Grilled room<br></div><div>NEARBY: Drongo’s Den, Holey Foot &amp; Tenth<br></div><div>NOTES: An okay RCP while it lasts!<br></div><div>Originally known as Casle’s Tomb but he was a shit member who caused a member serious grief and was more into graff so the name was fisted.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
