		<Placemark id="C23C47BFCB3E4617280A">
			<name>Fochenbeaver</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Fochenbeaver<br></div><div>GPS -37.836071, 145.128904<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 61 E-2<br></div><div>LOCATION: In Box Hill Golf Course (via Hay St) near the corner of Foch &amp; Beaver Streets<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: East<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 1.2m ⬜<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⭕<br></div><div>VALUE: ☹<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Tram 70 to end of line<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Gets bigger<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: Low bit at the start<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: 🙂<br></div><div>NEARBY: Gets Bigger, Blackburn, BLF &amp; Cro’s Tomb<br></div><div>NOTES: The drain goes to 2.1m instantly.<br></div><div>Fochenbeaver is named after the nearby streets. It was originally called Fucker Beaver.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
