		<Placemark id="D27D0996653E4617280A">
			<name>Fox Hole</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Fox Hole<br></div><div>GPS -37.729907, 144.925354<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 16 J-9<br></div><div>LOCATION: Just next to footbridge over Moonee Ponds Ck at the west end of Gaffney St<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2.4m ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ⭕<br></div><div>VALUE: 🙂<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Craigieburn train to Pascoe Vale<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: The stairway at the end<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: 🙂<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: 🙂<br></div><div>NEARBY: Five Mile Ck, DIPS &amp; Amex’s<br></div><div>NOTES: Fox Hole makes a good duo with The Falls. Do Falls second.<br></div><div>Fox Hole was named after the inlet… and also Samantha Fox (it’s not the 80s).<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
			<styleUrl>#__managed_style_0920FA33F53E916505AE</styleUrl>
