		<Placemark id="152363789103E4617280B">
			<name>Holey Foot</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description><![CDATA[<div>Holey Foot<br></div><div>🚫 🚲 🍸 🔑 🚫<br></div><div>GPS -37.749531, 145.069807<br></div><div>MELWAYS REF. 32 B-2<br></div><div>LOCATION: 7 Edgar St, Heidelberg<br></div><div>ENTRANCE: 2.2 / 2.4m (×2) ⭕<br></div><div>OTHER SHAPES: ☹<br></div><div>CLAN ZONE: North east<br></div><div>VALUE: ☹<br></div><div>PROBLEMS: ☹<br></div><div>TRANSPORT: Eltham train to Heidelberg<br></div><div>⛔: 🙂<br></div><div>HIGHLIGHT: Grilled end room<br></div><div>CLEANLINESS: 🙂<br></div><div>NEARBY: Fisted &amp; Satan’s<br></div><div>NOTES: This drain does end but it is locked and the old gap was repaired in 2018. Go back via other pipe.<br></div><div>Holeyfoot was first explored after visiting Russo in the Austin Hospital after he blew a hole through his foot.<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
