			<description>iD’s Tomb
🚫 🗝️
GPS: -37.891394, 145.096013
MELWAYS REF: 69 H-5
LOCATION: Just west of where Park Rd crosses Scotchman&apos;s Ck.
ENTRANCE: 1.9m 🎯
CLAN ZONE: South.
VALUE: 🗑️
TRANSPORT: Dandenong train to Oakleigh (dokily).
WATER: 🙂
PROBLEMS: Short crawl through low pipe.
HIGHLIGHT: Small redbrick section.
CLEANLINESS: 🙂
NEARBY: Mini Tenth, Dweller&apos;s Tomb &amp; Howza&apos;s Tomb.
NOTES: Not a very interested tunnel. Was Mile&apos;s Tomb.
iD&apos;s Tomb is named after the member who joined in the mid 90s.</description>
