			<snippet></snippet>
			<description>Jorgee’s Tomb
🚫 🍸
GPS: -37.801428, 144.822161
MELWAYS REF: 40 F-4
LOCATION: Near Pickersgill Ave on south west bank of Kororoit Ck.
ENTRANCE: 1.0m ⬜
OTHER SHAPES: ⚪
CLAN ZONE: South west.
VALUE: 🙂
TRANSPORT: Watergardens train to Sunshine.
WATER: 🙂
PROBLEMS: First 15 meters are low so pass 🍸 through grille.
HIGHLIGHT: First change.
CLEANLINESS: 🙂
NEARBY: Ash&apos;s Tomb, Stony Creek, 50th &amp; Not 50th.
NOTES: The low section is no problem. Apparently this drain changed a lot since this report was made.
Jorgee joined the Cave Clan in the late 80&apos;s and sadly the BDP in 2011.</description>
			<styleUrl>#__managed_style_05D0D2A5813E916505B0</styleUrl>
