			<description>C.O.A.D.
🚲
GPS: -37.66321, 144.941715
MELWAYS REF: 6 H-2
LOCATION: Follow creek against the flow from Barry Road.
ENTRANCE: 1.8m 🎯
CLAN ZONE: North.
VALUE: 🗑️
