			<snippet></snippet>
			<description>Cobra&apos;s Tomb
🚲* 🍸
GPS: -37.888684, 144.996725
MELWAYS REF: 67 C-5
LOCATION: East end of Bent Avenue.
ENTRANCE: 2m 3 x ⬜
OTHER SHAPES: ☹️
VALUE: 🙂
CLAN ZONE: South.
PROBLEMS: The outlet.
TRANSPORT: Sandringham train to Elsternwick.
