		<Placemark id="10770C91BF53E4617280E">
			<name>The Falls</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description>The Falls
🚫 ⓘ
GPS: -37.720197, 144.935781
MELWAYS REF: 17 A-6
LOCATION: Follow creek against flow from Arndt St.
ENTRANCE: 1.6m $\odot$
CLAN ZONE: North.
VALUE: 🙂
CLEANLINESS: $\ominus$
WATER: $\ominus$: $\odot$
TRANSPORT: Broadmeadows train to Pascoe Vale (go through fox hole).
HIGHLIGHT: The two waterfalls.
PROBLEMS: Boring once passed the waterfalls.
NEARBY: Fox hole, Dead, DIPS and Ayyy Flooded.
NOTES: Low for first 50 meters. Not really a shrinker. Turn back after falls.
The Falls (originally known as Bonus as it looked crap from the outside but was actually a bonus after doing Fox Hole) are renamed after a couple of nice waterfalls found not far inside the low tunnel.</description>
			<styleUrl>#__managed_style_05D0D2A5813E916505B0</styleUrl>
			<Point>
				<coordinates>144.935781,-37.720197,0</coordinates>
			</Point>
		</Placemark>
		<Placemark id="137697E32F63E4617280E">
			<name>Mega Stairway</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description>Mega Stairway
🚫 🧥 👁️
GPS: -37.959506, 145.0084
MELWAYS REF: 76 H-12
LOCATION: On beach opposite Royal Ave.
ENTRANCE: 1.6m ⚪
OTHER SHAPES: ⬜
CLAN ZONE: South.
VALUE: ☹️
HIGHLIGHT: Stairway.
WATER: ⊖: Tidal.
TRANSPORT: Train to Sandringham.
CLEANLINESS: Flooded entrance then rusty muddy walls.
PROBLEMS: Outlet is now submerged.
NEARBY: Gilligan&apos;s Tomb.
NOTES: Do at lowest tide. Exit via first safe manhole you can find beyond stairway or turn back (hence the ⓘ rating). The outlet is now submerged. Can be fun but IS Dangerous!!!
Mega Stairway was, at the time, the longest stairway known to the Clan.</description>
			<styleUrl>#__managed_style_05D0D2A5813E916505B0</styleUrl>
			<Point>
				<coordinates>145.0084,-37.959506,0</coordinates>
			</Point>
		</Placemark>
		<Placemark id="14FE7251CB13E4617280E">
			<name>Melbourne</name>
			<snippet></snippet>
			<description>Melbourne
🚫 🧥 👁️
GPS: -37.818897, 144.967675
MELWAYS REF: 1A J-12
LOCATION: Just upstream from City Tunnel.
ENTRANCE: 1.4m ⬜ x2
OTHER SHAPES: Balloon &amp; ⚪
VALUE: 🙂
CLAN ZONE: Inner.
TRANSPORT: Flinders St station.
WATER: ⊖: Tidal.
HIGHLIGHT: Being under easily the greatest city in Australia in a porn room.
CLEANLINESS: A bit messy.
PROBLEMS: Being seen. Getting passed waterfall.
NEARBY: City, Nylex, Nexus, Docklands, 69er &amp; Bob&apos;s Tomb.
NOTES: Melbourne&apos;s a good one for the hardcore explorers. It also has 2 outlets. Should it be rated higher?</description>
