	<Placemark id="0B8871A3A03CB8526C09">
		<name>Witch’s Tomb</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">Witch’s Tomb</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">GPS: 37.4404, 145.0447</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">LOCATION: In the creek next to Banyule Shared Trail, at Lower Plenty Road.</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">ENTRANCE: 2 x 1.5m ⭕</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">OTHER SHAPES:&nbsp;</span></span></span>▭<span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;"></span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">VALUE: 😐</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">CLAN ZONE: North east</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">CLEANLINESS: 🙂</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">TRANSPORT: Hurstbridge train to Rosanna, then bus to Kambea Cres/Lower Plenty Rd</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">HIGHLIGHT: Rooms</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">PROBLEMS: Low</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">NEARBY: Satan’s &amp; Holey Foot</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">NOTES: This drain is pretty low but has some really interesting rooms, side pipes and features. About 50 meters in there’s a small room with a side pipe and a sectioned off internal grill room above. Area above drain is under construction so most likely will change over time</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(222, 222, 222);"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;"><span class="font" style="font-family: AvenirNext-Medium;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 17px;">Witch’s Tomb is named after ‘Witch’ who mapped it.</span></span></span><br></p><div><br></div>]]></description>
